FORMAT: 1A
HOST: https://support.example.test

# Support API

Valid integration fixture for tickets and customer messages.

# Group Tickets

## Tickets Collection [/tickets{?state,priority}]

### List tickets [GET]
+ Parameters
    + state: open (string, optional) - Ticket state filter
    + priority: urgent (string, optional) - Priority filter

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (array[Ticket])

### Create ticket [POST]
+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (TicketCreate)

+ Response 201 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Ticket)

## Ticket Messages [/tickets/{ticketId}/messages]
+ Parameters
    + ticketId: ticket-100 (string, required) - Ticket identifier

### Add ticket message [POST]
+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (TicketMessageCreate)

+ Response 201 (application/json)
    + Attributes (TicketMessage)

# Data Structures

## Ticket (object)
+ id: ticket-100 (string, required)
+ subject: Cannot sign in (string, required)
+ state: open (string, required)
+ priority: urgent (string, optional)

## TicketCreate (object)
+ subject: Cannot sign in (string, required)
+ customerId: cust-42 (string, required)
+ priority: urgent (string, optional)

## TicketMessage (object)
+ id: msg-200 (string, required)
+ body: We are checking the account. (string, required)
+ authorId: agent-7 (string, required)

## TicketMessageCreate (object)
+ body: We are checking the account. (string, required)
+ authorId: agent-7 (string, required)
